pageProduct.name: Oral B Toothpaste Pro Health Advanced All Around Protection 110g
pageProduct.description:
General Information

ORAL-B PRO-HEALTH ADVANCED ALL AROUND PROTECTION.

Oral-B Pro-Health Advanced All Around Protection contains Active Stannous - Fluoride Complex that helps to provide multiple oral hygiene benefits.

For healthy gums and strong teeth.

Size: 110g

KEY FEATURES

• For healthy gums and strong teeth.
• WITH REGULAR BRUSHING, ORAL-B Pro-Health Advanced All Around Protection Toothpaste HELPS.
• Promote Gum Health.
• Fight Harmful Plaque.
• Whiten Teeth by Removing Surface Stains.
• Prevent Enamel Erosion.
• Fight Cavities, Fight Tartar, Fight Bad Breath.

Warnings

Do not swallow. Do not use this product in children 6 years of age or less. In case of intake of fluoride from other source, consult a dentist or doctor. Contains Sodium fluoride

Ingredients

Water, Sorbitol, Hydrated Silica, Sodium Lauryl Sulfate, Flavour, Carrageenan, Sodium Gluconate, Stannous Chloride, Xanthan Gum, Zinc Citrate, Sodium Hydroxide, Sodium Saccharin, Sodium Fluoride, Calcium Aluminium Borosilicate, Silica, CI 77891, CI 42090

Directions

Apply the product onto a soft bristled toothbrush. Brush teeth thoroughly at least twice a day (morning and evening) or as recommended by a dentist.
